<figureCitation id="E41CCA76D415CA815FB472C109E861F7" captionStart="Plate 2" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Plate 2. Otoliths of Leptolepis buttenheimensis and L. steberae. figs 1 - 7 Leptolepis buttenheimensis sp. nov. from the late Pliensbachian of Buttenheim; 1: holotype SNSB-BSPG 2022 IV 4, EPH horizon; 2 - 7: paratypes SNSB-BSPG 2022 IV 5 - 6; 2 - 5, 7: EPH horizon; 6: Apyrenum subzone. figs 8 - 12: Leptolepis steberae sp. nov. from the Pliensbachian of Buttenheim, EPH horizon; 8: holotype SNSB-BSPG 2022 IV 13; 9 - 12: paratypes SNSB-BSPG 2022 IV 14." figureDoi="10.3897/zitteliana.96.81737.plate2" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/671632" pageId="0" pageNumber="51">Plate 2, figs 8-12</figureCitation>
